description: Returns a list of end-to-end testing artifacts for a specified app, branch, and job. To return the build artifacts, use the GetJob API. For more information about Amplify testing support, see Setting up end-to-end Cypress tests for your Amplify application in the Amplify Hosting User Guide.

parameters.name: appId
parameters.description: The unique ID for an Amplify app.

parameters.name: branchName
parameters.description: The name of a branch that is part of an Amplify app.

parameters.name: jobId
parameters.description: The unique ID for a job.

nested_items.name: artifactFileName
nested_items.description: The file name for the artifact.

nested_items.name: artifactId
nested_items.description: The unique ID for the artifact.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: A pagination token. If a non-null pagination token is returned in a result, pass its value in another request to retrieve more entries.
